Stream on `/__zenith_dev/events` emits framed SSE events (`event: <name>
 data: {...}

`). Required invariants: - Every `build_start` is followed by exactly one `build_complete` or `build_error` with the same `buildId`. - `css_update` and `reload` are emitted only after `build_complete`. - `buildId` is monotonic across builds.
